 <section>
    <title>Installation</title>

    <para>The Raster library is header only, but depends on BOOST
    (<ulink url="http://www.boost.org">www.boost.org</ulink>) and GDAL (<ulink
    url="http://www.gdal.org">www.gdal.org</ulink>) that does require building
    and installation; follow the instructions on the BOOST web pages.
	The version of BOOST that is used is 1.57.</para>

    <para>The library makes use of C++11 language and standard library
    features. These are not yet universally supported. The suggested platform
    is Microsoft Visual Studio 2013.</para>
  </section>
